@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .calculator {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 300px;
  }

  .calculator-button {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
}
```

Test on various device sizes and orientations to ensure the calculator remains usable and visually appealing.

